---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Poetry & Calligraphy" description="Explore Chinese poetry - Tang Dynasty verses, Song lyrics, and the meditative art of calligraphy.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 via-indigo-600 to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="text-blue-200 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Literature</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Poetry & Calligraphy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">In ancient China, poetry was not just literature—it was the highest art form, practiced by emperors and peasants alike.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/poetry/tang" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📜</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Tang Poetry</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">The golden age of Chinese poetry—Li Bai's flights of fantasy, Du Fu's social conscience.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/poetry/song" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎋</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Song Lyrics</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">The Song Dynasty innovation—poetry set to music, from Su Shi's bold verses to Li Qingzhao's grace.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/poetry/calligraphy" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✒️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Calligraphy</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Where writing becomes art—the four styles of calligraphy from seal script to cursive.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/poetry/poets" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">👤</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">The Poets</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Biographies of China's greatest wordsmiths and the stories behind their masterpieces.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-8">Featured Articles</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-indigo-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🌙</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Li Bai's "Quiet Night Thought" - Full Analysis</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Line-by-line translation and cultural context of China's most famous moon poem.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-400 to-purple-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🖌️</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Chinese Calligraphy for Beginners</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Start your journey with the four calligraphy styles, essential tools, and first strokes.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-400 to-slate-700 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">📝</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Du Fu: China's Greatest Poet</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">The life and legacy of the poet who captured the human condition.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
